PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1289 - TRITICONAZOLE) by setting maximum limits (MRLs) on residues of this product (a) resulting from its use as a fungicide on barley, oats and wheat, and (b) remaining in milk, eggs and other food made with the meat of animals who were exposed to it in their feed.
